8. Re-Usable Code
We present here a minimal, end to end flow you can paste into a Jupyter cell. It pulls the same public data sources, computes the three CIA sub scores, and produces the risk column exactly as the paper does. The code cell can be in Python (or any language supported by the kernel) statements, imports, func-tion definitions, plots, etc.

